configure adds -Werror which triggers several deprecation warnings to become errors:
CFLAGS="${CFLAGS} -Wall -Werror -std=c99 -Wmissing-prototypes"
The -Werror needs to be removed from that line in configure{.in,}.
The indentation warning triggered by -Wall was a false alarm as well.
I've applied the patch to F-24/25 and Rawhide, and kicked off builds on the latter two.
